node.text:
Does your #UPPAbabyVISTA need some TLC after all of your winter strolls ? Our Tune-UP Gear-UP Expert, Sam Osborne has all of the tips and tricks clean your VISTA wheels and keep you strolling smoothly all winter long!❄️ Tip: volume up!🔊
 
Looking for more info to help at-home Tune-UP's? Connect directly with our Tech Experts and schedule your virtual Tune-UP Gear-UP at the link in bio today!

node.text:
Welcoming our newest addition, GREYSON CRUZ V2! 🖤🤎

This fashion is a modern twist on a timeless classic pairing two neutral tones, black and brown. The fabric is detailed in charcoal mélange with a two-tone effect that adds depth while delivering a sense of comfort.

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Looking to use your #UPPAbabyMINU from birth? With the From Birth Kit accessory, you can easily transform your stroller into an ideal resting place for your newborn to lie flat and comfortably stroll.

Features include: 
• Extendable UPF 50+ sunshade
• Five-point harness for added security
• Easily folds with the stroller

Let’s welcome NOA, the newest VISTA V2 fashion.
 
NOA is a rich, classic navy in a new woven material, carbon frame, and saddle leather!
 
Check out the fashion-inspo for this chic, classic style:
• NOA Navy is sophisticated core and classic color with timeless style, yet contemporary and sporty feel when layered with the tinted charcoal black frame.
• Inspired by fashion collections in Paris, Milan, London, and New York!

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Planning a fun summer getaway? Pack your #UPPAbabyVISTA and hit the road! Want to learn our recommendations on the best way to easily fold, carry, and store your stroller into your vehicle? Check out this video to learn more!
 
1. Activate brake
2. Extend handlebar to the highest position
3. Recline seat to 2nd most upright position, forward-facing position
4. Pull up on two release triggers and rotate handlebar to ground
